Description
-----------

This command reloads both the [material
declaration](Material_%28decl%29 "Material (decl)") and corresponding
texture images for the surface currently in the crosshairs.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    reloadSurface

Parameters
----------

This command does not accept parameters.

Notes
-----

This command is useful when testing a material shader on a surface in
game.

You can make small changes to a material in general, point your
crosshairs at the surface in game, and use this console command to see
the effect of those changes.

